_sText:
This is the fifth map I have ever made, and I got the idea for it from a friend.
in each room there are 3-4 teleports, one on each side. The teleports are not random, but go to each room as if you were walking through a door. In the rooms surounding the center, there are arrows for cover and direction. In the middle is a small room inside the room.
Have fun finding the secret...

Please contact me if you wish to alter this map in any way.

Thank You
-Me
